  <thing id="cHellreavr" name="Hellreaver" description="Devils and their ilk can go only so far before their actions demand a response. At some point, a devil will destroy enough lives that someone has to take a stand. That someone is often a hellreaver&#151;a warrior whose outrage at the actions of the fiends and their ability to corrupt and seduce without consequence fuels an array of combat abilities. These potent options make these warriors tremendously effective combatants of the baatezu.\n\n{b}Special Requirements{/b}\nMust slay an outsider with the evil subtype.\n\n{b}Source{/b}: Fiendish Codex 2" compset="ClassLevel" maxlimit="10">
    <usesource source="FCodex2"/>
    <tag group="ClassType" tag="Prestige"/>
    <bootstrap thing="cHelpHel"></bootstrap>
    <link linkage="helper" thing="cHelpHel"/>
    <pickreq thing="fPowerAtt"/>
